12:11.481 --> 12:14.276
- SIR, WOULD YOU
LIKE MORE COFFEE?

12:14.276 --> 12:16.736
- OH. WELL,
THANK YOU, MA'AM.

12:16.736 --> 12:18.363
- YOU WANT SUGAR IN THAT?

12:18.363 --> 12:21.116
OR IF IT'S TOO HOT,
I COULD BLOW ON IT.

12:21.116 --> 12:22.785
- YOU KNOW WHAT'S WEIRD?
- HMM?

12:22.785 --> 12:25.745
- SITTING IN A FAMILY DINER
WITH AN ERECTION.

12:25.745 --> 12:27.372
- I'LL KEEP THAT IMAGE
IN MIND

12:27.372 --> 12:29.875
WHILE I'M CLEARING PLATES
OF FRIED EGGS.

12:34.504 --> 12:36.298
- IF HE'S GONNA ENJOY
OUR AIR CONDITIONING ALL DAY,

12:36.298 --> 12:38.758
HE'S GOT TO ORDER
MORE THAN AN ENGLISH MUFFIN.

12:38.758 --> 12:40.302
- I'LL MAKE HIM
HAVE PANCAKES.

12:40.302 --> 12:42.554
- LOOKY YOU.
YOU'RE GLOWING, GIRL.

12:42.554 --> 12:44.681
IT MUST BE
ALL THAT GOOD SEX.

12:44.681 --> 12:46.558
- BEST PART
IS THERE'S NO DRAMA,

12:46.558 --> 12:48.476
WHICH USUALLY JUST
MEANS I'M BORED.

12:48.476 --> 12:50.395
BUT INSTEAD,
I THINK I'M JUST HAPPY.

12:50.395 --> 12:51.897
- WE'RE GLAD FOR YOU.

12:51.897 --> 12:53.773
LET US KNOW
HOW WEEK TWO GOES.

12:57.360 --> 12:59.196
- [chuckles]

13:04.869 --> 13:07.913
- I, UM--I MADE--UH,

13:07.913 --> 13:09.748
I OPENED AN ACCOUNT
HERE YESTERDAY.

13:09.748 --> 13:10.957
NAME'S FRANK GALLAGHER.

13:10.957 --> 13:12.167
- SECURITY?

13:12.167 --> 13:13.543
- UH, MR. GALLAGHER.

13:13.543 --> 13:14.794
I'LL--I'LL TAKE THIS,
LINDSAY.

13:14.794 --> 13:16.254
THANK YOU.
WE'RE FINE.

13:16.254 --> 13:17.505
UH, CAN I GET YOU ANYTHING?

13:17.505 --> 13:18.924
COFFEE?
DANISH?

13:18.924 --> 13:20.717
- NO.
WHAT KIND OF DANISH?

13:20.717 --> 13:22.845
- HERE.
SIT.

13:22.845 --> 13:26.097
GO.

13:26.097 --> 13:28.976
SO, UH, WHERE DID WE LEAVE OFF?

13:28.976 --> 13:32.980
OUR, UH, PREMIUM MONEY MARKET
IS AT 1.65.

13:32.980 --> 13:35.732
BUT SAY WE PAIR YOU
WITH A FINANCIAL MANAGER,

13:35.732 --> 13:37.609
PERSONALIZE YOUR PORTFOLIO,

13:37.609 --> 13:41.029
FOCUS ON YOUR LONG-TERM
FINANCIAL GOALS, YOUR--

13:41.029 --> 13:43.531
YOUR PLAN FOR RETIREMENT?

13:43.531 --> 13:45.325
- I WANT TO MAKE
A WITHDRAWAL.

13:45.325 --> 13:46.534
- WHAT?
- MY MONEY.

13:46.534 --> 13:47.744
I WANT TO GET IT.

13:47.744 --> 13:48.871
- WE DON'T HAVE IT.

13:48.871 --> 13:49.955
- HOW'S THAT?
- YOU--

13:49.955 --> 13:51.790
YOU WITHDREW IT YESTERDAY.

13:51.790 --> 13:53.416
WE--WE HAD TO SEND OUT
TO THAT OTHER BRANCH

13:53.416 --> 13:55.252
FOR THOSE HUNDREDS.

13:55.252 --> 13:57.879
IT'S NOT EVERY DAY SOMEONE
WANTS $121,000 IN CASH, SO...

13:57.879 --> 13:59.839
- I GOT ALL OF IT?
- YES.

13:59.839 --> 14:01.591
BUT IF YOU'D LIKE
TO LEAVE A PORTION

14:01.591 --> 14:03.218
OF YOUR SETTLEMENT WITH US
TO INVEST, WE'D CERTAINLY--

14:03.218 --> 14:06.513
- DID I HAPPEN TO SAY WHERE I
WAS GOING WHEN I LEFT HERE?

14:06.513 --> 14:09.975
- NO.

14:09.975 --> 14:11.643
- I SAY ANYTHING AT ALL?

14:11.643 --> 14:14.437
- JUST THAT YOU WERE GOING
TO CELEBRATE.

14:14.437 --> 14:16.439
I TAKE IT YOU HAD FUN.

14:31.496 --> 14:32.706
- DEBBIE.

14:32.706 --> 14:33.873
HOW WAS YOUR PARTY?

14:33.873 --> 14:36.459
ALLY'S COUSIN TOLD US
ABOUT IT.

14:36.459 --> 14:38.378
- IT WAS FUN.
- MAYBE NOT SO FUN

14:38.378 --> 14:41.464
FOR THE BOY YOU RAPED.
NEVER HEARD OF THAT.

14:41.464 --> 14:43.967
A GIRL WHO HAD TO RAPE A BOY
TO GET LAID.

14:43.967 --> 14:48.013
HOW DOES THAT WORK?
[laughter]

14:48.013 --> 14:53.018
[grunting]

14:53.018 --> 14:54.311
- GET THE FUCK OFF ME.

14:54.311 --> 14:56.021
[grunting]

14:56.021 --> 14:57.022
- HEY, WHOA.

14:57.022 --> 14:58.023
WHOA, HEY.

14:58.023 --> 14:59.649
GET OFF.

14:59.649 --> 15:01.192
HEY.
HEY, WHOA.

15:01.192 --> 15:03.695
HEY.
CUT IT--

15:03.695 --> 15:05.488
COME ON.
FOUR ON ONE, THAT'S NOT COOL.

15:05.488 --> 15:07.198
- NONE OF YOUR
FUCKING BUSINESS.

15:07.198 --> 15:08.993
- YEAH? WHY DON'T YOU FIND
FOUR OTHER GIRLS TO FIGHT?

15:08.993 --> 15:11.161
I'LL LET YOU TEAR
EACH OTHER'S EYES OUT.

15:11.161 --> 15:14.080
OTHERWISE BEAT IT.

15:14.080 --> 15:16.082
- RAPIST BITCH.

15:20.879 --> 15:24.299
- THAT--THAT WAS THE NICEST
THING ANYONE'S EVER DONE FOR ME.

15:24.299 --> 15:25.383
- YOU OKAY?

15:25.383 --> 15:27.011
- YEAH.

15:27.011 --> 15:28.845
- LOOK, I SAW YOU THROW
THE FIRST PUNCH.

15:28.845 --> 15:30.638
IF YOU'RE GONNA
START A FOUR-ON-ONE LIKE THAT,

15:30.638 --> 15:35.060
YOU BETTER PICK UP SOME MOVES
'CAUSE THAT WAS PATHETIC.

15:35.060 --> 15:37.145
- WAIT!
WHAT'S REFLEX ATHLETICS?

15:37.145 --> 15:40.148
[rock music]

15:40.148 --> 15:48.114
♪ ♪

15:48.114 --> 15:50.325
- WHAT ARE YOU WORKING ON?

15:50.325 --> 15:52.077
- A VIDEO GAME.

15:52.077 --> 15:53.745
I WRITE MUSIC
FOR VIDEO GAMES.

15:53.745 --> 15:55.372
- YOU DIDN'T TELL ME THAT.
THAT'S COOL.

15:55.372 --> 15:57.166
- YOU WANT COOL?
OKAY.

15:57.166 --> 15:59.876
WELL, UH, THIS GAME
IS CALLED "HAM SCRAMBLE."

15:59.876 --> 16:01.294
IT'S FOR AGES 4 AND UP.

16:01.294 --> 16:03.254
YOU HAVE TO SMASH
AS MANY LITTLE PIGS AS POSSIBLE

16:03.254 --> 16:05.090
WITH A BIG PURPLE HAMMER.

16:05.090 --> 16:06.716
- WHAT MUSIC GOES WITH THAT?

16:06.716 --> 16:09.010
- OH, I'M CREATING
A MOVING STREAM MOTIF

16:09.010 --> 16:12.764
AS A REMINDER
OF OUR OWN MORTALITY.

16:12.764 --> 16:15.058
IT PLAYS EVERY TIME ONE OF THE
LITTLE GREEN PIGS GETS CRUSHED.

16:15.058 --> 16:18.937
- THE PIGS ARE GREEN?
- THEY ARE.

16:18.937 --> 16:21.314
DID I MENTION THAT I'M
FALLING IN LOVE WITH YOU?

16:21.314 --> 16:23.108
- NO.

16:23.108 --> 16:26.861
UH, THANK YOU.

16:26.861 --> 16:30.240
- YEAH, I JUST, UH--
I WASN'T GONNA SAY ANYTHING.

16:30.240 --> 16:32.117
A THOUGHT THAT I HAD.

16:32.117 --> 16:35.079
[chuckling]

16:35.079 --> 16:38.748
GO AWAY, NOW IT'S AWKWARD.

16:38.748 --> 16:41.668
UH, MORE COFFEE, PLEASE.
- UH.

16:41.668 --> 16:43.169
- THANKS.

16:48.175 --> 16:54.056
[phone ringing]

16:54.056 --> 16:55.640
- HI.
- WHATEVER TIME

16:55.640 --> 16:58.101
YOU GET OFF WORK TONIGHT,
YOU'RE GOING DANCING.

16:58.101 --> 17:00.645
AND IF YOU HAVE OTHER PLANS,
YOU'RE GONNA CANCEL.

17:00.645 --> 17:02.147
- ANYTHING ELSE?
- YOU CAN'T BRING

17:02.147 --> 17:04.108
YOUR NEW BOYFRIEND.

17:04.108 --> 17:05.442
- OKAY.
- IT'S NOT NEGOTIABLE,

17:05.442 --> 17:06.901
SO DON'T TRY IT.

17:06.901 --> 17:08.528
I NEED TO GET DRESSED UP
LIKE A SEX OBJECT

17:08.528 --> 17:10.780
AND BE OBJECTIFIED,
NOT BE THE THIRD WHEEL

17:10.780 --> 17:12.323
TO YOU
AND YOUR NEW SQUEEZE.

17:12.323 --> 17:14.075
IN FACT, I DON'T EVEN WANT
TO HEAR ABOUT HIM.

17:14.075 --> 17:17.579
NOT HOW GREAT HE IS OR HOW MANY
TIMES AN HOUR YOU BANG IT OUT.

17:17.579 --> 17:19.914
GOING THROUGH A SEX FAMINE
OVER HERE.

17:19.914 --> 17:21.374
- YOU KNOW WHAT
HE JUST TOLD ME?

17:21.374 --> 17:22.792
- WHAT DID I JUST SAY?

17:22.792 --> 17:24.711
- THAT HE'S FALLING
IN LOVE WITH ME.

17:24.711 --> 17:26.421
- DAMN.
- I MEAN,

17:26.421 --> 17:28.173
WE'VE ONLY BEEN
SEEING EACH OTHER A WEEK.

17:28.173 --> 17:30.425
- YOU DIDN'T SAY IT BACK,
DID YOU?

17:30.425 --> 17:32.136
- NO.
- GOOD GIRL.

17:32.136 --> 17:33.178
- BUT I'M, LIKE, FREAKING OUT.

17:33.178 --> 17:34.095
I MEAN, I'M--I'M--

17:34.095 --> 17:35.597
I'M STANDING BY THE REGISTER,

17:35.597 --> 17:39.559
AND I'M, LIKE, TINGLING.

17:39.559 --> 17:41.561
HELLO?

17:41.561 --> 17:44.273
- OH, HELL, YEAH.
THERE HE IS.

17:44.273 --> 17:47.108
[cheering]

17:47.108 --> 17:50.195
I ALWAYS TOOK YOU FOR A NICKEL
AND DIMING CHEAPSKATE, FRANK.

17:50.195 --> 17:53.240
BUT LAST NIGHT, YOU
RESTORED MY FAITH IN HUMANITY.

17:53.240 --> 17:55.408
RAISE THEM UP TO FRANK.
all: YEAH!

17:55.408 --> 17:58.077
- TAKE IT I BOUGHT
A FEW ROUNDS LAST NIGHT.

17:58.077 --> 17:59.871
- YOU PRACTICALLY BOUGHT
THE BAR, FRANK.

17:59.871 --> 18:01.372
AND NOT THE CHEAP STUFF.

18:01.372 --> 18:03.708
NOTHING OUT OF
PLASTIC BOTTLES.

18:03.708 --> 18:05.627
- WHAT DID I SPEND?

18:05.627 --> 18:07.545
- COUPLE GRAND, MAYBE.

18:07.545 --> 18:11.175
- COUPLE OF GRAND.
JESUS FUCK.

18:11.175 --> 18:13.593
DID I HAPPEN TO SAY WHERE I
WAS GOING WHEN I LEFT HERE?

18:13.593 --> 18:15.262
- I WAS PASSED OUT
BY THEN, FRANK.

18:15.262 --> 18:16.846
- DAMN. SOUNDS LIKE I
MISSED A GOOD TIME.

18:16.846 --> 18:18.097
- YEAH.

18:18.097 --> 18:21.601
YEAH.
- WHAT'S WRONG, FRANK?

18:21.601 --> 18:25.188
- SEARCHING THE DEEPEST RECESSES
OF MY MEMORY LOOKING FOR A CLUE

18:25.188 --> 18:29.276
TO THE WHEREABOUTS
OF A LOST FUCKING FORTUNE.

18:29.276 --> 18:30.485
- AH, YOU MISPLACED A 20,
DID YOU?

18:30.485 --> 18:31.819
THAT'S TOO BAD.
- [laughs]

18:31.819 --> 18:33.905
TRY CHECKING YOUR POCKETS.
- RIGHT.

18:33.905 --> 18:36.407
LIKE I'M NOT GONNA
REALIZE I'M--

18:36.407 --> 18:39.410
HOLD ON.

18:43.081 --> 18:45.291
- HOLY SHIT.
THAT SAYS PORSCHE.

18:45.291 --> 18:47.794
- YOU STOLE A PORSCHE?

18:47.794 --> 18:49.879
- I MIGHT HAVE BOUGHT ONE.

19:03.268 --> 19:06.188
- IS THIS WHERE YOU
LEARNED TO FIGHT?

19:06.188 --> 19:07.480
- NAH.
I LEARNED IN JUVIE.

19:07.480 --> 19:09.148
AFTER I GOT RAPED
THREE OR FOUR TIMES,

19:09.148 --> 19:11.193
I FIGURED I SHOULD PICK UP
A FEW MOVES.

19:11.193 --> 19:13.237
- REALLY?
- NO.

19:13.237 --> 19:16.489
- UM, I--
I WANT TO LEARN HOW TO FIGHT.

19:16.489 --> 19:19.243
I THOUGHT MAYBE YOU
COULD TRAIN ME.

19:19.243 --> 19:22.829
- WHAT, LIKE KARATE KID? WAX ON.
- WAH.

19:22.829 --> 19:24.331
- LOOK, THIS IS CHICAGO.
YOU WANT TO FIGHT?

19:24.331 --> 19:26.333
PUNCH THE OTHER GIRL IN THE TIT.
YOU WANT TO BOX?

19:26.333 --> 19:28.252
YOU TAKE A CLASS.
- I CAN'T AFFORD A CLASS.

19:28.252 --> 19:32.130
- THEY'LL GIVE YOU
A TRIAL CLASS FOR FREE.

19:32.130 --> 19:34.132
ASK AT THE DESK.

19:41.306 --> 19:43.516
- TINY TIM, YOU UP.

19:43.516 --> 19:45.643
- WELCOME TO 14th AND MAIN.
I'LL BE YOUR SERVER.

19:45.643 --> 19:46.978
WHAT WILL YOU BE HAVING?

19:54.986 --> 19:57.322
- THE FUCK YOU GIVE HIM?
- WHAT?

19:57.322 --> 19:59.157
- THE MAN GAVE YOU A 20.

19:59.157 --> 20:00.742
THAT'S A QUARTER GRAM.

20:00.742 --> 20:02.369
YOU GAVE UP A TEENER.

20:02.369 --> 20:03.995
THAT'S 1.5.

20:03.995 --> 20:06.581
NOW YOU OWE ME A HUNDRED BUCKS.
- WHAT?

20:06.581 --> 20:09.709
- OUT HERE, NIGGERS GET SHOT
FOR THIS SHIT.

20:09.709 --> 20:12.712
SO YOU BETTER FIND A WAY
TO GET ME PAID.

20:12.712 --> 20:15.715
[rap music]

20:15.715 --> 20:19.427
♪ ♪

20:54.921 --> 20:57.048
- HUH?
- AH, JESUS.

20:57.048 --> 20:59.425
KERMIT,
WHAT ARE YOU DOING BACK THERE?

20:59.425 --> 21:00.510
- RESTING.

21:00.510 --> 21:03.638
OH, WHAT A NIGHT, HUH?

21:03.638 --> 21:05.181
- YOU WERE WITH ME LAST NIGHT?

21:05.181 --> 21:06.516
- YOU DON'T REMEMBER?

21:06.516 --> 21:08.393
- WHAT HAPPENED
AFTER THE ALIBI?

21:08.393 --> 21:09.894
LEAVE OUT NOTHING.

21:09.894 --> 21:12.271
- WELL, YOU BOUGHT THIS CAR
FROM BOBBY FARING.

21:12.271 --> 21:13.815
60 GRAND AND CHANGE.

21:13.815 --> 21:15.233
- 60.

21:15.233 --> 21:16.651
FUCK.

21:16.651 --> 21:19.278
SO THAT LEAVES 61
MINUS THE ALIBI.

21:19.278 --> 21:21.030
CALL IT 59.

21:21.030 --> 21:22.490
- AND THEN YOU BOUGHT CRACK.

21:22.490 --> 21:25.284
AND I-I DIDN'T WANT ANY,
SO YOU DID IT ALL.

21:25.284 --> 21:27.496
AND WE DROVE TO CHINATOWN
FOR DIM SUM.

21:29.247 --> 21:31.500
- OH, YOU MADE IT.

21:31.500 --> 21:33.209
- HI, YEAH.
THANKS FOR HAVING ME.

21:33.209 --> 21:35.504
IT'S, UH, NICE TO SEE YOU.
HEY.

21:35.504 --> 21:38.673
- YOU HAVE MY 10 GRAND, RIGHT?
NO? OKAY.

21:38.673 --> 21:41.092
WELL, LET'S JUST CALL IT,
LIKE--LIKE 4% INTEREST.

21:41.092 --> 21:44.388
SO WHAT WOULD THAT BE? LIKE--
- JASON.

21:44.388 --> 21:48.141
- THIS IS ADORABLE MARSHA
AND HER NANNY, YOHANIA.

21:48.141 --> 21:50.685
ADORABLE WENDY
AND HER NANNY, THAIS.

21:50.685 --> 21:52.311
EVERYONE, THIS IS LIP.

21:52.311 --> 21:53.563
- GUYS.
- YOU HUNGRY?

21:53.563 --> 21:55.356
YOHANIA CAN MAKE
YOU A QUESADILLA.

21:55.356 --> 21:56.983
- OH, NO.
NO, I'M OKAY.

21:56.983 --> 22:00.319
THANK YOU, THOUGH.

22:00.319 --> 22:01.904
THEY, UH--
THEY EACH HAVE A NANNY?

22:01.904 --> 22:03.407
- YES. AND I KNOW
YOU WANT A QUESADILLA.

22:03.407 --> 22:04.782
YOU SAID
YOU WERE STARVING EARLIER.

22:04.782 --> 22:06.451
- OH, NO. YOHANIA,
SHE'S GOT ENOUGH TO DO.

22:06.451 --> 22:07.869
- SHE'S NOT A SLAVE.

22:07.869 --> 22:09.704
SHE'S A NANNY.

22:09.704 --> 22:12.665
DAD, ARE YOU LOCKING THE WINE
FRIDGE BECAUSE LIP IS HERE?

22:12.665 --> 22:14.417
- PLEASE DON'T PICK A FIGHT.

22:14.417 --> 22:16.002
- WELL, HE NEVER LOCKS IT.

22:16.002 --> 22:18.337
YOU SAID DOUCHEBAGGERY
WOULD NOT BE A PROBLEM.

22:18.337 --> 22:20.131
- WELL, IF YOU MET
MY DAD, YOU KNOW, YOU, UH--

22:20.131 --> 22:21.340
YOU REALLY
WOULDN'T SWEAT IT.

22:21.340 --> 22:22.633
- I'LL MAKE US COCKTAILS.

22:22.633 --> 22:24.927
- RIGHT.

22:27.180 --> 22:30.183
[dance music plays]

22:30.183 --> 22:33.519
♪ ♪

22:33.519 --> 22:35.313
- NOW THIS IS WHAT
I'M TALKING ABOUT.

22:35.313 --> 22:38.400
DRINKING, DANCING,
GUYS LOOKING AT MY ASS.

22:38.400 --> 22:39.692
DO YOU SOME GOOD, TOO.

22:39.692 --> 22:40.985
- WHAT DO YOU WANT?
VODKA SODA?

22:40.985 --> 22:42.528
- VODKA VODKA.

22:42.528 --> 22:46.575
OH.
YES, SIR.

22:46.575 --> 22:48.493
- TWO VODKA SODA.

22:48.493 --> 22:56.542
♪ ♪

23:29.742 --> 23:32.036
- NO, NO, NO, NO, NO, NO.
KEEP DOING THAT.

